<item>
            <title>[PIG-4530] StackOverflow in TestMultiQueryLocal running under hadoop20</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4530</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you run the command &lt;tt&gt;ant -Djavac.args=&quot;-Xlint -Xmaxwarns 1000&quot; clean jar test-commit&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
as indicated here &lt;a href=&quot;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/PIG/HowToContribute&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/PIG/HowToContribute&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The result is a failed build caused by Stack overflow due to an unintended infinite recursion in setting up the MiniCluster.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks like the cause is that  &lt;tt&gt;shims/test/hadoop20/org/apache/pig/test/MiniCluster.java&lt;/tt&gt; does not override the &lt;tt&gt;static public Launcher getLauncher()&lt;/tt&gt; method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
